text: Enele Sosene Sopoaga PC (born 10 February 1956) is a Tuvaluan politician. He was the 12th Prime Minister of Tuvalu from 2013 until 2019."Tuvalu Parliament elects new Prime Minister Sopoaga" , Radio New Zealand International, 5 August 2013 ==References== ==Other websites== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of Tuvalu
title: Enele Sopoaga
